column2: I want just wish my life had some meaning
Maybe a friend can help me find my place...
Maybe I need a change of routine...
Maybe I just need to keep soul searching...

I've been trying hard to find something that I can dedicate my life to. I've been considering becoming a {{#if noun}}{{noun}}{{/if}}{{#unless noun}}{{name}}{{/unless}} but, frankly, don't know if I'm up for it
I will try my hand at being a {{#if noun}}{{noun}}{{/if}}{{#unless noun}}{{name}}{{/unless}}
